Package: @PACKAGE@
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: @MAINTAINER@
Depends: adduser, init-system-helpers
Recommends: systemd
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Homepage: @HOMEPAGE@
Description: Rust edge reverse proxy for small and medium deployments
 rginx is a Rust edge reverse proxy focused on HTTP/HTTPS ingress,
 API gateway fronting, gRPC ingress, hot reload, graceful restart,
 health checking, rate limiting, and local observability.
